  "title": "Supernatural Crops",
  "description": "A Mystical Agriculture esque mod for fabric ",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oW2hElr.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1903\" height=\"688\" /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Supernatural Crops is meant to be a version of Mystical Agriculture for Fabric. This mod adds in bushes that grow various ores.</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Pictures</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ee5vdSQ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" /><br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/egXP4oL.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" /><br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DeZ8DXI.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">How To Use</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>First use a Netherite Hoe on stone to make scraped stone&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"blob:https://imgur.com/b8fb44e7-5d1c-4f6c-b786-5629d2afb354\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vIVXm8t.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" />&nbsp;<br />Then go to the end and mine some Embedded Abyss to get Seeds Of The Abyss to craft your seeds<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GafKNes.png\" width=\"1113\" height=\"626\" /><br />And lastly just simply plant your seeds!<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9vWNhGN.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1070\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;<br /><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Recipes</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>Coal Bush Seeds<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WJgyzz3.png\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /><br />Iron Bush Seeds</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9DAiUJA.png\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /><br />Gold Bush Seeds<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iWphkxZ.png\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /><br />Diamond Bush Seeds<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ho58i0X.png\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /><br />Emerald&nbsp;Bush Seeds<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FLvvavz.png\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /><br />Netherite Bush Seeds<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ahu4DrD.png\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /><br />Lapis Lazuli&nbsp;Bush Seeds<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Bz7i0S1.png\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /><br />Redstone&nbsp;Bush Seeds<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zaqEHXR.png\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">These next recipe's only apply if nuggets are enabled:<br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Diamond</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XaeKkXd.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Emerald</span><br /></span><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0Y7geSD.png\" /></p>\n<p>Netherite Scrap<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AbLhUxO.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/608088354042544139/766012374754787328/Ol1Tcf8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"84\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Community:</span></p>\n<p><a title=\"My Discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/Epf6ffw2da\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.freepnglogos.com/uploads/discord-logo-png/concours-discord-cartes-voeux-fortnite-france-6.png\" width=\"101\" height=\"101\" /></a><a title=\"My YouTube\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyzsPpD0PPB7FQy93Yo6xfQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zIpE3Ub.png\" width=\"105\" height=\"74\" /></a><a title=\"My Twitch\" href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/fusion_flux\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://assets.stickpng.com/thumbs/580b57fcd9996e24bc43c540.png\" width=\"106\" height=\"106\" /></a><a title=\"My Twitter\" href=\"https://twitter.com/TheFusionFlux\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7WSfFBH.png\" width=\"108\" height=\"81\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Check out my other mods!</span><br /><a title=\"FluxTech\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fluxtech\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VEqE5rn.png\" alt=\"FluxTech\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></a><a title=\"Origins: Umbrellas\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/origins-umbrellas\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q4FeOQ6.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></a></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If you ask for a forge port ill add your kneecaps to <strong><em>the collec</em><em>tion!~</em></strong></p>",
